# Cursor AI Rules
rules:
  - "Always use Java 17 and Groovy 4 syntax."
  - "When generating code, prefer Spock for Groovy tests and JUnit 5 for Java tests."
  - "Ensure compatibility between Groovy and Java classes."
  - "Use meaningful method names and include minimal docs in Java."
  - "Suggest refactorings to reduce boilerplate in mixed Java/Groovy projects."
